{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"90c8c9aeff","title":"中央工作委员会在刘少奇主持下进行工作","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d839bc1ec3","index":0,"year":1947,"month":3,"day":30,"articleId":"90c8c9aeff","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"贺龙","id":"d0a2337495","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji4.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"277bf3191c","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"77ba770f82","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":18,"text":"这是毛泽东、任弼时给晋绥军区司令员贺龙转周恩来的电报。"},{"id":"098d3f51cd","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":33,"text":"朱、刘，指朱德、刘少奇。"},{"id":"371ae8cdab","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":59,"text":"董，指董必武，当时任中共中央工作委员会常委。叶，指叶剑英，当时任中共中央后方委员会书记。"},{"id":"4a94cd4acc","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":4,"part_index":2,"offset":147,"text":"毛、周、弼，指毛泽东、周恩来、任弼时。"},{"id":"b9f264818d","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":5,"part_index":2,"offset":172,"text":"两延，指延长、延川。"},{"id":"c9f5a6992d","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{},"index":6,"part_index":2,"offset":201,"text":"安定，今子长县。保安，今志丹县。"}],"contents":[{"id":"024eb89a11","type":"title","text":"中央工作委员会在刘少奇主持下进行工作","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77ba770f82","type":"appellation","text":"贺龙同志即转恩来：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"098d3f51cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）中央决定组织中央工作委员会，在少奇主持下进行各项工作。朱、刘二同志明晚由石咀驿（绥德南七十里）动身去临县与董、叶诸同志会合，经五台往太行。中央直属机关人员已至晋西北者，照前议一部往太行，一部就地疏散，由你告董、叶处理，嗣后听候中央工委指示。（二）接电后请你于数日内回来，嗣后即由毛、周、弼三人主持中央。我们现在石咀驿附近。（三）敌已占两延，下一步行动待侦。（四）如敌攻清涧，我们准备移至安定、保安之间。为免被敌隔断，故请你早回河西，河东事由刘、朱、董、叶处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"371ae8cdab","type":"paragraph","text":"毛弼","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a94cd4acc","type":"paragraph","text":"寅三十申","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"90c8c9aeff","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":247,"end":247}}}},"__N_SSG":true}